query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(ci mi_idx n t it2) NoMergeJoin(ci it2 mi mi_idx n t it1) */ select min(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
min(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
min(t.title) AS movie_title
from name AS n
inner join cast_info AS ci
on n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'f' AND n.name like '%Smith,%' AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
'(producer)')
inner join title AS t
on t.id = ci.movie_id
inner join movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
on t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
inner join info_type AS it2
on it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'votes'
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
inner join info_type AS it1
on it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'budget';
